gujlish: Hu to vichari rahyo hato ke apde movie jovay jaiye.

english: Do you want to try that new restaurant nearby?
gujlish: Tane navi restaurant try karvi chhe je najik ma chhe?

english: Let’s relax at home and binge some series.
gujlish: Chalo ghar e relax kariye ane kai series joiye.

english: I heard there’s a concert in town this weekend.
gujlish: Mane sambhalyu chhe ke aa weekend ma concert chhe shaher ma.

english: We can go for a long drive and have dinner outside.
gujlish: Apde ek long drive par jaiye ane bahar dinner kariye.

english: I just started a new HIIT workout, and I feel amazing.
gujlish: Hu navi HIIT workout sharu kari chhu, ane maja avi rahi chhe.

english: Have you tried the new protein shake at our gym cafe?
gujlish: Tame tamara gym cafe ma navi protein shake try kari chhe ke?

english: My endurance has improved a lot since I started training regularly.
gujlish: Jyaare thi hu regular training karo chhu, mara endurance ma khub sudhar thayo chhe.

english: Let’s set up a new gym challenge for the month.
gujlish: Chalo aa mahine mate navi gym challenge set kariye.

english: I’m trying a new yoga routine to complement my workouts.
gujlish: Hu gym workout ne complement karva mate navi yoga routine try kari rahyo chhu.

english: We should join that weekend boot camp together.
gujlish: Apde aa weekend boot camp sathe join karie.

english: I read about a recovery method that really works after heavy workouts.
gujlish: Hu ek recovery method vishe vachyu chhe je heavy workouts pachi sachu kaam kare chhe.

english: Have you noticed how much more energy you have post-workout?
gujlish: Tame jovo chho ke workout pachi ketli moti energy male chhe?
